commitResults.messageTitle: Renamed bot. Added greet and exit.
Added statements to allow echoing of commands and exit with command bye.
Added ListOfTask. Added add and list functionality.
Added Task class. Added mark as done / undone functionality.
Change the way to do tasks are added, allowing tasks that consist of several words to be inputted.
Update exception handling by including more exception cases considered, and add delete functionality.
Update EXPECTED.TXT and input.txt with the test cases considered, and have minor changes to the formatting of ChaCha.java and ListOfTask.java.
Update ChaCha.java to check if data file chacha.txt exists and create one otherwise

ChaCha.java: Update to fix reading of chacha.txt file ListOfTask.java: Update with copyFile method which will read and save each task into the ArrayList tasks Task.java: Update constructor to take in isDone as argument DeadlineTask.java: Update constructor to take in isDone as argument ToDoTask.java: Update constructor to take in isDone as argument EventTask.java: Update constructor to take in isDone and date as argument

ListOfTask.java: Fix reading file bug and add update chacha.txt functionlity after respective command DeadlineTask.java: Change access modifiers for fields EventTask.java: Change access modifiers for fields Task.java: Add fields needed to update chacha.txt file
